Description: Rime schema: Hakka Huiyang dialect (Hagfa Pinyim)
 Input method data for typing Hakka in the Huiyang dialect using
 the Hagfa Pinyim romanization. Toneless input is accepted by default;
 tone digits 1-6 are optional for disambiguation.
